(42, 1, 77, 41, 1, 3, 4, 'remission of their sins', 'Connection of Remission of Sins', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of remission of sins. Luke 1:77 speaks of knowledge of salvation through the remission of sins, while Mark 1:4 mentions baptism of repentance for the remission of sins.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
